title: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? classSet is not expected
description: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? The output is "MySomeClass".
OB: When calling the ServletContainerInitializer onStartup() method with a Set of Class objects as a parameter, the output is "MySomeClass".
EB: The expected behavior is that the output should not be "MySomeClass".
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Create a ServletContainerInitializer
2. Call the onStartup() method with a Set of Class objects as the parameter
3. Observe the output, which should not be "MySomeClass".
